#1962
oasis wyrm boss aquifer wyrm deep spring~
@@lOasis Wyrm@@N~
@@lThe Oasis Wyrm raises its mineral-scaled head from the spring vent with the attention of something that has not seen a warm-blooded creature in this deep in a long time.@@N
~
The Oasis Wyrm is the sole reason the Great Oasis still functions as a spring-fed water source. It arrived in the East Cistern as the flooding began, found the deep spring vents, and has been here since — incidentally maintaining them through its habitation. Killing it will drain the springs within a season. It is not evil. It is simply here, in the place that suits it, and it defends that place with the force appropriate to its size.
~
